   APPLE-RESURGENCE (Cupertino, Calif.) _ Apple Computer, which was
all but given up for dead a few years ago, has had a remarkable
resurrection. Eleven days ago, the company exceeded analysts'
estimates in reporting its sixth consecutive profitable quarter. By
John Markoff. With photo and graphic.
