   RIVAL-MAGAZINES-MEDIA (Undated) _ Esquire and GQ, nominees for
National Magazine Awards this week, are rival men's publications
headed by two former colleagues and sharing a demonstrated interest
in what might politely be called male anatomy. But they approach
the subject _ as they do many other things _ very differently. By
Alex Kuczynski.
