<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-26 02:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2990 &Cx1f; tic-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BWAY-AZR &LR;      04-26 1338
