<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
BC- ELIMINATE_ELIMINATE-AZR
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   Budgeted Washington  &UR; QUAYLE will not move in Monday's Arizona
Republic report.
</P>
