<HEADLINE>
BOTH A VICTIM OF RACIAL PROFILING _ AND A PRACTITIONER 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(lh) 
 By STEVEN A. HOLMES   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ The spring day was bright and sunny enough for
sunglasses, yet cool enough to require a sweatshirt and baggy sweat
