logical progression for the Internet, which has brought us instant
messaging, electronic commerce and CD-quality music for the
downloading. Social activism has always strived for getting a
message to the masses and what better, more efficient way is there
than e-mail? (Gallaga, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED
</P>
