<P>
   Moved as BC-TRIGGER-HAPPY-AMERICA-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; AT 50, NATO IS TOO YOUNG FOR RETIREMENT &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
