<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DANUBE-DEBRIS-NATO-RESEND-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DANUBE BLOCKED BY NATO RUBBLE; RIVER TRAFFIC HALTED  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
