TV-SWEEPS _ (Los Angeles) _ The May sweeps period promises to have
the usual stunts, farewells by two long-running series, ``Mad About
You'' and ``Home Improvement,'' and plenty of cliffhanger endings.
By Marla Matzer. &QL;
