   _ Reading a Publishers Weekly story about well-wishers who
helped the San Francisco bookstore Cover to Cover move, &UR; Bud &LR; 
 &UR; Johns &LR;  was amused to see that volunteer  &UR; Mauricio Vela &LR;  was
identified as ``executive director of the nearby Banal Heights
Neighborhood Center.''
