<DOCNO> NYT19990426.0472 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-26 22:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4197 &Cx1f; ttg-z
a k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GRIMES-HUMOR-COLUMN-$     04-26 0772
